        "ggpjZRuk_E2_text": "12x Back Pain Relief Patches",
        "ggvGL5-tdwy_text": "<strong>Soothe back pain naturally</strong> with our herbal relief patches! Made from 100% <strong>natural ingredients</strong>, they promote muscle relaxation, easing tension and soreness. Simple to apply and brings freeing <strong>relief for up to 12 hours.</strong>",
        "ggyEKece8hY_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-70e0977e-0f27-4256-b14f-dd4bb3ddf6a3.jpg"
