        "ggP5xbHg6z-_text": "<p><strong>After 15 minutes: </strong>Turn your head freely. Look down without pain. Stand taller.</p>",
        "ggP9YY587P1_text": "<p><strong>30 Seconds–5 Minutes: </strong>Heat floods the area with nutrient-rich blood while traction maintains crucial disc space. You feel muscles finally releasing their death grip.</p>",
        "gg_-MJSPsBq_text": "<p><strong>0–30 Seconds: </strong>Feel immediate decompression as vertebrae gently separate. That crushing pressure on your nerves? Gone.</p>",
