        "gg1-nBNIy9D_text": "<p>\"My neck pain was getting unbearable, and the hump at the base of my neck kept getting bigger. Sitting at work, looking down at my phone-<strong>everything hurt.</strong> I bought the Triple Fusion Neck Massager out of desperation, and after <strong>just 1 week</strong>, the relief blew me away. The tightness eased, the burning down my neck stopped, and <strong>I can finally turn my head without that sharp pinch.</strong> Even my neck hump looks visibly smaller. I use it every day now. If you're unsure, trust me… this thing WORKS!\"</p>",
